<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>hū qiú ā bà 迦南790</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 hū qiú ā bà hū qiú ā bà,
 nǐ de shēn tǐ qǐ néng ràng chóu dí jiàn tà.
 hū qiú ā bà hū qiú ā bà, nǐ de
 ér nǚ zài qí dǎo. jīng guò le dōng xià,
 jīn tiān míng bái le. shì chóu dí bǎ bài zi sā.
 dì xiōng a, qiān bēi hé yī, shén de jiā cái néng zhuàng dà.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>790</hymn_number>
</song>